content: wtfsayo: Focused on enhancing the ElizaOS plugin registry, merging three PRs including a significant update to improve v1 compatibility detection and prevent semver issues in elizaos-plugins/registry#199, and adding repository metadata and new plugins in elizaos-plugins/registry#198 and elizaos-plugins/registry#197. Their work primarily involved feature development and bug fixes, with changes across configuration and code files.
